snippet.title: Amber Hayes, MD, Renown Medical Group discusses Sports Injury Prevention and Recovery.
snippet.description:
Dr. Amber Hayes with Renown Medical Group at Los Altos discusses sports injury prevention, sports physicals, and what to do if you have an injury. 

A native of northern Nevada, Amber Hayes, MD, is a graduate of the University of Nevada, School of Medicine.  Her interests include women's health, sports medicine, nutrition, and preventative medicine.
